    <h1>Privacy Policy for SEO-Pro Shopify App</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>

    <p>Thank you for using <strong>SEO-Pro</strong>, a Shopify app designed to help merchants enhance their store’s SEO performance and compress product images. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you install and use the SEO-Pro app, we may collect the following data:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Store name, store URL, and owner email.</li>
      <li>SEO metrics: performance, accessibility, best practices, and SEO scores.</li>
      <li>Product details like titles, descriptions, and images.</li>
      <li>Image files for compression and optimization.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information solely to provide and improve the app’s functionality, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Analyzing and displaying SEO metrics and reports.</li>
      <li>Compressing and optimizing product images.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties.</p>

    <h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <p>We use secure servers and encrypted storage. All transmissions are done over HTTPS. Access is limited to authorized personnel only.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>Data is retained only while the app is installed. Once uninstalled, we delete all associated data within <strong>30 days</strong>.</p>

    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your data. You can request this by contacting us using the details below.</p>

    <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We may use trusted third-party tools for SEO analysis and image optimization. These tools do not store or misuse your data.</p>

    <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy. Changes will be posted on this page with the updated effective date.</p>

